title: Bullish Two Hundred Day Moving Average Cross - WMK - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Weis Markets, Inc. (Symbol: WMK) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $42.18, changing hands as high as $42.54 per share. Weis Markets, Inc. shares are currently trading up about 2.9% on the day.
